OL,3,CWhat Trump told ITV News about the
OL,4,Creopening of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FBy US Correspondent Dan Rivers and
OL,7,FWashington News Editor Jonathan Wald
OL,9,FUS President Donald Trump is currently
OL,10,Fin Nevada, but he is monitoring the
OL,11,Fsituation in the Middle East closely.
OL,13,FNews had just broken minutes earlier
OL,14,Fthat the Strait of Hormuz had been
OL,15,Freopened by the Iranians.
OL,17,FI wanted to get his first reaction and
OL,18,Fclarity about what this means for
OL,19,FAmerica's blockade of Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
