OL,3,CWhat Trump told ITV News about the
OL,4,Creopening of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FHe was clear, telling me: "I feel
OL,7,Fgood. Too bad we didn't have help from
OL,8,FNato - paper tiger! Too bad we didn't
OL,9,Fhave help from Nato, we did this
OL,10,Famazing thing (referring to the
OL,11,Fmilitary campaign against Iran)."
OL,13,FHe went on to tell me the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz is "not open as it pertains to
OL,15,FIran, because we have to finish the
OL,16,Fdeal first, it's open for everybody
OL,17,Felse."
OL,19,FThis suggests the US blockade of
OL,20,FIranian ports and oil will remain for
OL,21,Fnow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
