OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776453069
OL,3,CWhat Trump told ITV News about the
OL,4,Creopening of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FWhen I asked him where this leaves his
OL,7,Frelationship with the UK and
OL,8,Fspecifically Sir Keir Starmer, he was
OL,9,Fblunt.
OL,11,F"Not good, not good at all."
OL,13,FNews of the partial opening of the
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz has already sent
OL,15,Fstock markets around the world
OL,16,Fvaulting higher.
OL,18,FThe Dow Jones Industrial Average
OL,19,Fopened up more than 1.3 %, and the
OL,20,FFTSE index in London also moved
OL,21,Fsharply higher on the news.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
