PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776453069
OL,3,CWhat Trump told ITV News about the
OL,4,Creopening of the Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThere is still much detail to work out
OL,7,Fbefore a comprehensive deal with Iran
OL,8,Fcan be made.
OL,10,FBut for now, Trump sounded pleased
OL,11,Fwith progress, but it is clear from
OL,12,Four conversation that the president
OL,13,Fthinks the crisis in the Middle East
OL,14,Fis not over yet.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
